{"tid":1791542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉國謙：本港公務員廣義上是國家幹部","createTime":"2019-12-21T02:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T06:42:41.000Z","uid":125168,"like":25,"dislike":358,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"5622fef8ad7ad4068430ce3ae98082abe163ef06","tid":1791542,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T02:37:32.000Z","msg":"葉國謙：本港公務員廣義上是國家幹部<br />\n<br />\n全國人大代表葉國謙表示，現時本港公職人員在招聘時，需要對《基本法》有一定認識，但他認為，一些高級公務員，除了要認識《基本法》，亦要對憲法有所了解，因為在廣義上，公務員都是中華人民共和國下的國家幹部。葉國謙在本台節目《星期六問責》表示，將來若香港公務員要晉升，亦可以參考澳門的做法，需重新考核對《基本法》的認識，但只需作為其中一個考核環節，不必程序化，以免令不懂《基本法》和憲法的人失去機會。<br />\n<br />\n2019-12-21 10:25:06 (1)"},{"pid":"bf89984a6f1cb6e6644253267d7f9f59af866375","tid":1791542,"uid":125168,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T02:38:27.000Z","msg":"聽日有聲援維吾爾族集會<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/izCNXiQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FizCNXiQ.jpg&h=f7d28be1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"453152787231584860b6f92e0d6c154223f93ef2","tid":1791542,"uid":125168,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T02:38:57.000Z","msg":"搞教育界，下步好快搞公務員<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2811badbbb3f1cc8190d0b4b7a7166acb18abbf2","tid":1791542,"uid":511,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T02:39:49.000Z","msg":"Agger 專幹人民的娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36caa151bd8a1d4d9ccad413aa07b008ef46d6d1","tid":1791542,"uid":57659,"like":121,"dislike":1,"score":120,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T02:40:08.000Z","msg":"再廣義啲大家都係地球人<br />\n點解要管撚住香港"},{"pid":"1f9a49a31ca3679bdb6984d6d9eec7f45457954a","tid":1791542,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T02:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49cefcf0ff43819e100c6cf23267aefe59936f04","tid":1791542,"uid":127466,"like":78,"dislike